<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. David lengpa khawpi achun,
 Gan In tawmtak a um a;
 Ziechun a nun Nausen a siel,
 Gankuong zalkhun a mangin;
 Chunnu nunnem chu Mari,
 A cha chuh Isu Krista.

[V2]
 2. Van apatin leiah A hung,
 Pathien Lalte Lal ahi;
 A kingakna gan In tawm hi'n,
 A puon luoi gankuong ahi;
 Gimthei, chagah liengvai in,
 Leiah Hukdampa a um.

[V3]
 3. A naupan lai hun cheng cheng khan,
 Mi a zahin, thu a ngai;
 A nu Amah hun dawntei chuh,
 A hehpihin, A enkawl;
 Kristien naupang cheng cheng le,
 Amah bangin um chiet un.

[V4]
 4. Amah umdan zuih ding ahi,
 Ei bang' nichengin A khang
 Neu, hatlo, panpihbei ahi,
 Kah leh nuih ei bang A hei;
 I lungkham ei thawk pih a,
 I kipah ei kipah pih.

[V5]
 5. A tawpleh I mitun mui tiu,
 A hehpih tatna ziekin;
 Zie Naupang ching leh ngaihum chuh,
 Vana I Lalpau ahi;
 A chiehna mun lam zuonin,
 A chate A puizel hi.

[V6]
 6. Gan In tawm, a sika bawngchal,
 Dinna mun hita loin;
 Van a chun Amah chu mui tiu,
 Pathien khut changlam achun;
 Puon vam silhte um vela,
 Chawihat a A um tieng leh.</lyrics>
<title>ONCE IN ROYAL DAVID'S CITY</title>
<hymn_number>60</hymn_number>
</song>